# =============================================================================
# config/flatpak-packages.list — Flatpak applications to install and update
#
# Format: <app-id>  [# description]
# Lines starting with # are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
#
# App IDs use reverse-domain notation (e.g. org.gimp.GIMP)
# Run: flatpak search <name>  to find app IDs
# =============================================================================

# ── Currently no Flatpak apps installed on this machine ───────────────────────
# Add apps here to manage them. Example:
# org.gimp.GIMP                 # GNU Image Manipulation Program
# org.inkscape.Inkscape         # Vector graphics editor
# com.spotify.Client            # Spotify music player
# org.videolan.VLC              # VLC media player
